  "title": "Dreamy Sweet British Peppers Trifle",
  "description": "A romantic British dessert featuring mixed peppers and candy, made with ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly ingredients. This trifle is a unique blend of salty, chewy, and sweet flavors.",
