  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Roast the mixed peppers in the oven for 30 minutes.",
    "Let the peppers cool down to room temperature.",
    "Layer the roasted peppers, crushed candy canes, and crushed ginger snaps in a large bowl.",
    "Mix the whipped cream, honey, lemon juice, vanilla extract, and salt in a separate bowl.",
    "Pour the cream mixture over the layered ingredients in the bowl.",
    "Refrigerate the trifle for at least 2 hours before serving.",
    "Serve the trifle chilled and enjoy."
